{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"12cb066d35","title":"毛泽东等祝贺保加利亚社会主义革命二十一周年的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"850d847a73","index":0,"year":1965,"month":9,"day":8,"articleId":"12cb066d35"}],"tags":[{"id":"29143cbd32","name":"无产阶级国际主义","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"a7ea3bd8ce","name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"321aa70a95","type":"title","text":"毛泽东等祝贺保加利亚社会主义革命二十一周年的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"121f8072b2","type":"paragraph","text":"索非亚保加利亚共产党中央委员会第一书记、保加利亚人民共和国部长会议主席托·日天科夫同志，保加利亚人民共和国国民议会主席团主席格·特莱科夫同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"af14ef5efb","type":"paragraph","text":"在保加利亚社会主义革命二十一周年的时候，我们向你们，向兄弟的保加利亚人民致以热烈的祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"f908ff8195","type":"paragraph","text":"中保两国人民的友谊有着深厚的基础。维护和加强这种友谊符合我们两国人民的共同愿望。中国人民将一如既往，在马克思列宁主义和无产阶级国际主义的基础上，为加强中保两国人民的友谊和团结而继续努力。祝保加利亚人民在建设社会主义的事业中取得新的成就。祝中保两国人民的友谊日益巩固和发展。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"f5718e9b2a","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会主席毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"8466b25b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"0e2a3b2933","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国主席毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"1429d88b53","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"e31839876e","type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民代表大会朱德","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"d8c789c46d","type":"paragraph","text":"常务委员会委员长朱德","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"150f1243a5","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国国务院总理周恩来","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"},{"id":"630d67e39d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六五年九月八日","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35"}],"page":{"id":"8ed3103ce8","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"12cb066d35","start":190,"end":190}}}},"__N_SSG":true}